## Rules
- The criterion must capture the GENERAL lesson, not the specifics of any one case (no company names, industries, or one-off details).
- It must be actionable for a scoring agent: phrased as guidance on what to reward or penalize.
- Pick exactly ONE existing dimension (by its exact name) that the criterion belongs to.
- One sentence, maximum two.

## Output Format
Respond with a valid JSON object in this exact format:
{
  "target_dimension": "<exact name of one existing dimension>",
  "amendment_text": "<the new scoring criterion>",
